{"tid":1389568,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［游擊戰］和理非都可以幫手！","createTime":"2019-07-31T02:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T02:38:49.000Z","uid":113155,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3af6d70df29f4a5a3c5f46a5cf2872d6c7fae967","tid":1389568,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:32:33.000Z","msg":"兩千年前孫武用既疲兵戰略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1387842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1387842</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n親愛的前線，首先真係無言感激你哋嘅付出！<br />\n我想提小小建議，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">游擊戰</span></span> <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非人都可以有參與機會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">和理非：</span><br />\n1<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 求下你哋，日日黑衫full gear番工番學同行街</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線已經犧牲咗咁多，我哋又唔敢上前線，拜託大家幫幫手，唔好淨係識去行下，行完番歸睇直播啦！<br />\nFull gear出街對前線幫助真係好撚大，起碼唔洗發完夢就掉gear。gear短缺，千金難買啊！捐錢備佢哋食飯，不如<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">買gear自己著出街</span></span>。又唔犯法，抄牌咪抄囉，你又唔會上前線，怕咩備人抄！<br />\n<br />\n2 幫手游擊戰，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰略</span></span>：<br />\n如果目測，咦！而條街有好多黑衣人喎，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5</span></span>50up先好做。<br />\n暗號：（光復香港，時代革命！）<br />\n聽到有人叫，我哋即和應，然後搵一條最近嘅紅綠燈，由綠燈坐到紅燈，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">直至犬黎。一見到犬，頭也不回，即作鳥獸散。</span></span> <br />\n而個可能需要同哨小隊商討到時點睇水。<br />\n遍地開花，撚死狗！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">前線巴打：</span></span><br />\n和理非啲死人性格，一定唔會主動出擊。<br />\n1 麻煩你哋到時清清喉嚨，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">幫手大叫暗號，同埋叫人出去一齊過馬路</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2 如果有犬，你哋對開防暴犬，催淚彈食到厭，槍聲聽到免疫，相信啲藍衫犬對你哋黎講小case，唔撚識驚。但和理非見到藍衫犬，一撚定好驚。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">麻煩到時幫手疏散和理非，定一定佢哋小鹿亂撞嘅心。</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n親愛的前線，如果冇目標，就唔好再守啦。<br />\n612 第一次正式大型警民衝突<br />\n71 垃圾會<br />\n721 愛國愛黨徽<br />\n呢啲有目標，正！<br />\n728 見到真係有樽頸位，又折損咁多手足，好撚心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊幫手打游擊好唔好？一黎真係好溫和，唔會有暴力場面備cctvb影到，二黎成本低，就算捉到，我相信點都唔會判到有罪！<br />\n<br />\n如果有其他意見，歡迎一齊討論！<br />\nTg谷<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/playwiththedog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fplaywiththedog&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij3wORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=88b6acf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/playwiththedog</a>"},{"pid":"4f4dca716d855065e54597eba62675f48ba7e379","tid":1389568,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:32:57.000Z","msg":"自推先"},{"pid":"b507d03d8cdc6032790157be5426a8798ad9697d","tid":1389568,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:35:16.000Z","msg":"要多人知先可以玩到啊游擊戰！"},{"pid":"daf8831de707f53fa812e8e7ad3046dd14755bfb","tid":1389568,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:36:56.000Z","msg":"和理非，唔好再坐以待斃"},{"pid":"fa56d0fdc1be56eaf070ada38864e2e4d45d9d6b","tid":1389568,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:38:49.000Z","msg":"番工人士驚就帶多套晒換，收工先全黑！<br />\n諗下前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋唔心痛咩"}]}